Question 8: Checking Electricity Bill Slabs
Write a Python program that takes the number of electricity units consumed and calculates the bill:
•	If units are less than 100, charge ₹2 per unit.
•	If units are between 100 and 300, charge ₹5 per unit.
o	If units are more than 200, apply a 10% surcharge.
•	If units are above 300, charge ₹8 per unit with a 20% surcharge.
