Question 9: Mobile Data Plan Recommendation
Write a Python program that asks the user for their monthly internet usage (in GB) and suggests a plan:
•	If usage is less than 2GB, suggest "Basic Plan - ₹199/month."
•	If usage is between 2GB and 10GB, suggest "Standard Plan - ₹499/month."
o	If usage is above 7GB, suggest "Add ₹100 for extra data."
•	If usage is more than 10GB, suggest "Premium Plan - ₹999/month."
