Question 10: Admission Eligibility for a Course
Write a Python program that takes a student's marks in Mathematics and Science as input and checks:
•	If both subjects have marks above 70, print "Eligible for admission."
o	If both are above 90, print "Eligible for scholarship."
•	If one subject is below 70, print "Eligible for reconsideration."
•	If both are below 70, print "Not eligible for admission."
