Question 11: Movie Ticket Pricing Based on Age and Time
Write a Python program that takes the age of a person and the time of the movie (morning/evening) and decides the ticket price:
•	If age is below 12, charge ₹100.
o	If it's an evening show, charge ₹150.
•	If age is 12 or above, charge ₹200.
o	If it's an evening show, charge ₹300.
