Question 12: Weather-based Clothing Suggestion
Write a Python program that takes the temperature (in °C) as input and suggests clothing:
•	If temperature is below 10°C, suggest "Wear a heavy jacket and gloves."
•	If temperature is between 10°C and 20°C, suggest "Wear a sweater and jeans."
o	If it's also raining, suggest "Carry an umbrella."
•	If temperature is above 20°C, suggest "Wear light clothes."
